-- Cinven Shifts Registration to Guernsey, Financial News Reports
-- B y   A n n e - S y l v a i n e   C h a s s a n y
-- 2012-03-05T13:36:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-05/cinven-shifts-registration-to-guernsey-financial-news-reports.html
Cinven Ltd., the British private-
equity firm, is moving its management vehicle offshore to the
tax haven of Guernsey, Financial News  reported  today, citing a
source close to firm.  Cinven is changing from a limited company into a U.K.-based
limited liability partnership, with all of its 18 partners and a
few other individuals becoming members, the publication said on
its website. Cinven declined to comment to Financial News.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Anne-Sylvaine Chassany in London at 
 achassany@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
